description: Magical Five is a sentai outfit consisting of Yuuma (Pink), Pachira (Black), Liru (Red), Aiko (Blue) and Keimii (Green). Together, they pilot the giant robot M5 in their fight for justice. Pink, Black and Green tend to be a little dense when it comes to putting a plan into action, so their fights typically end in humiliating defeat...
name: Magical Five
